headline: Spotting Winners: Ingersoll Rand (NYSE:IR) And Gas and Liquid Handling Stocks In Q3
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Ingersoll Rand (NYSE:IR) and the rest of the gas and liquid handling stocks fared in Q3.
